{"tid":2386063,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[GME] 談北極星船務之戰","createTime":"2021-01-29T10:51:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T10:55:09.000Z","uid":442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"02eaa8f854b91798dde15d1d0bc4fad420dc6c54","tid":2386063,"uid":442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:51:56.000Z","msg":"大時代入面有呢幕<br />\n<br />\n因為北極星船務捲入同英國政府既官司，被華人交易所主席陳萬賢瘋狂沽空致價格閪迷<br />\n<br />\n而當時佢既對手方進新打算同佢決一死戰，就聯同幾位時任富豪hold 哂手上既北極星股票（buy and hold)<br />\n<br />\n決戰當日重點放左係中午官司結果度，中午前陳萬賢瘋狂沽，方進新瘋狂接，結果接到市面上既流通股全數被方進新接哂，官司結果出爐果不其然北極星敗訴，陳萬賢正打算低價平倉之濟市場上並無股票比佢買（貨源歸邊）<br />\n<br />\n陳萬賢心知不妙馬上召開記者會表示有大量假股票係市場流通，企圖造低個市令自己可以低價入貨<br />\n<br />\n可惜市場上所有股票已經比方進新買入，陳萬賢只有眼白白看著手上的沽空（白頭片）被搾乾<br />\n<br />\n事情發展到最後本應是方進新大勝，但最後卻因為丁蟹被間接毒打而報復，方進新被打致七孔流血昏迷。<br />\n<br />\n我愛大時代<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AFebCST.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAFebCST.png&h=be8aecfa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZAx1fEz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZAx1fEz.png&h=03ca391f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vx8f4xV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVx8f4xV.png&h=0473364b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3BxTRcW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3BxTRcW.png&h=4f88b12e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4UdotZC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4UdotZC.png&h=d948ed86&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LfkmZ6i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLfkmZ6i.png&h=1340d8e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gxJS6Mj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgxJS6Mj.png&h=11d7782e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y6KCyrm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2